{"type":"message","id":"a8160559","parentId":"cc24469a","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:40:04.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了一些错误：\n1. `fcitx-sogoupinyinhxm ABI Version Error` - 这是搜狗输入法的组件ABI版本错误，可能是版本不兼容\n2. `fcitx-keyboard-us already exists` - 键盘输入法重复\n3. `sgim_gd_cell.bin copy fail` - 搜狗皮肤文件复制失败\n\n让我检查一下搜狗输入法的配置和版本问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"6c8505e649cb1470fb98c5c9b20a541532e8769e8baca187441e729b794b2395"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uh1shjo2gg6d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 搜狗输入法版本 ===\" && sogou-qimpanel --version 2>&1 || dpkg -l sogoupinyin && echo -e \"\\n=== 皮肤文件 ===\" && ls -la ~/.config/sogoupinyin/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"无配置目录\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1019,"output":187,"cacheRead":25344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26550,"cost":{"input":0.0003057,"output":0.00022439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00076032,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00129042}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774579198865,"responseId":"061520ffe39d58f3f1390e572c28c87f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4ae6d9e","parentId":"a8160559","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:40:04.715Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uh1shjo2gg6d_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 搜狗输入法版本 ===\n/bin/bash: 行 1: sogou-qimpanel: 未找到命令\n期望状态=未知(u)/安装(i)/删除(r)/清除(p)/保持(h)\n| 状态=未安装(n)/已安装(i)/仅存配置(c)/仅解压缩(U)/配置失败(F)/不完全安装(H)/触发器等待(W)/触发器未决(T)\n|/ 错误?=(无)/须重装(R) (状态，错误：大写=故障)\n||/ 名称           版本         体系结构     描述\n+++-==============-============-============-=================================\nii  sogoupinyin    4.2.1.145    amd64        Business Sogou Input Method\n\n=== 皮肤文件 ===\n总计 20\ndrwxrwxr-x  5 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  9月 10  2025 .\ndrwx------ 51 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  3月 23 13:48 ..\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  3月 27 10:39 conf\ndrwxrwxr-x  5 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  9月 10  2025 dict\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  9月 10  2025 log"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":66,"aggregated":"=== 搜狗输入法版本 ===\n/bin/bash: 行 1: sogou-qimpanel: 未找到命令\n期望状态=未知(u)/安装(i)/删除(r)/清除(p)/保持(h)\n| 状态=未安装(n)/已安装(i)/仅存配置(c)/仅解压缩(U)/配置失败(F)/不完全安装(H)/触发器等待(W)/触发器未决(T)\n|/ 错误?=(无)/须重装(R) (状态，错误：大写=故障)\n||/ 名称           版本         体系结构     描述\n+++-==============-============-============-=================================\nii  sogoupinyin    4.2.1.145    amd64        Business Sogou Input Method\n\n=== 皮肤文件 ===\n总计 20\ndrwxrwxr-x  5 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  9月 10  2025 .\ndrwx------ 51 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  3月 23 13:48 ..\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  3月 27 10:39 conf\ndrwxrwxr-x  5 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  9月 10  2025 dict\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 zhangyanbo zhangyanbo 4096  9月 10  2025 log","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774579204712}}
{"type":"message","id":"eecf1594","parentId":"b4ae6d9e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:40:13.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"环境变量配置看起来正确，搜狗也安装了。问题可能出在：\n1. ABI版本错误 (fcitx-sogoupinyinhxm)\n2. 某些GTK/Qt应用没有正确继承环境变量\n\n让我检查一下 nautilus 重启后是否能正常工作，或者尝试在终端中启动 nautilus 看看是否有错误。\n\n实际上，问题可能是 nautilus 运行时没有加载输入法。需要检查是否需要重启 nautilus 或者在启动时设置环境变量。\n","thinkingSignature":"f3bf593bdad23bfe6a909ee1c1ec1a44674a90e39cf6b66e01f6fc4e7809ee8c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_75zg6hcxrstq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 重启 nautilus ===\" && nautilus -q && sleep 1 && echo \"nautilus 已退出\" && echo -e \"\\n=== 检查日志 ===\" && journalctl --user -u nautilus --no-pager -n 20 2>/dev/null || echo \"无日志\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":482,"output":193,"cacheRead":26304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26979,"cost":{"input":0.0001446,"output":0.0002316,"cacheRead":0.0007891199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0011653199999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774579204716,"responseId":"06152104761f3f6f78fd55225829ed55"}}
