{"type":"message","id":"b7f7e4d2","parentId":"b1ba1674","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:42:27.982Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zd32ptqon2vx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 nautilus 依赖 ===\n\tlibgtk-4.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libgtk-4.so.1 (0x00007df2f5800000)\n\tlibportal-gtk4.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libportal-gtk4.so.1 (0x00007df2f6301000)\n\n=== GTK4 immodule ===\n总计 52\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 11月 19 19:15 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root  4096 11月 10 09:32 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 43176  3月 21  2025 libim-ibus.so"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":29,"aggregated":"=== 检查 nautilus 依赖 ===\n\tlibgtk-4.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libgtk-4.so.1 (0x00007df2f5800000)\n\tlibportal-gtk4.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libportal-gtk4.so.1 (0x00007df2f6301000)\n\n=== GTK4 immodule ===\n总计 52\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 11月 19 19:15 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root  4096 11月 10 09:32 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 43176  3月 21  2025 libim-ibus.so","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774579347979}}
{"type":"message","id":"c95db0dd","parentId":"b7f7e4d2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:42:37.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到问题了！nautilus 使用的是 GTK4，而当前系统没有 GTK4 的 fcitx immodule！这就是问题的根源。\n\nGTK4 的 immodule 目录只有 libim-ibus.so，没有 fcitx 的。\n\n解决方案：\n1. 安装 fcitx 的 GTK4 支持（如果有的话）\n2. 或者降级 nautilus 使用 GTK3\n3. 或者使用其他文件管理器（如 Thunar, Nemo 等，它们可能使用 GTK3）\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"e93d03bb923f94b3424c58243cb2b02498629fed9775d6bc8e7c5f7e1d4f21d7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到问题了！🎯\n\n**问题根源：**\n- 你的 `nautilus` 使用的是 **GTK4**\n- 系统只有 GTK2/GTK3 的 fcitx immodule，**没有 GTK4 的 fcitx 支持**\n- 所以在 GTK4 应用中无法调用搜狗输入法\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_34y7pyrqxvk7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查是否有 GTK4 fcitx 支持 ===\" && apt-cache search fcitx | grep -i gtk4 && echo -e \"\\n=== 检查 nautilus 可用版本 ===\" && apt-cache policy nautilus 2>/dev/null | head -10","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":334,"output":253,"cacheRead":31040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31627,"cost":{"input":0.0001002,"output":0.0003036,"cacheRead":0.0009311999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013349999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774579347983,"responseId":"0615219455337277d9436a434a427f1f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a64c1f3","parentId":"c95db0dd","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:42:38.155Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_34y7pyrqxvk7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查是否有 GTK4 fcitx 支持 ===\nfcitx5-frontend-gtk4 - GTK4 IM Module for fcitx5\n\n=== 检查 nautilus 可用版本 ===\nnautilus:\n  已安装：1:48.0-1ubuntu1\n  候选： 1:48.0-1ubuntu1\n  版本列表：\n *** 1:48.0-1ubuntu1 500\n        500 http://cn.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu plucky/main amd64 Packages\n        100 /var/lib/dpkg/status"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":916,"aggregated":"=== 检查是否有 GTK4 fcitx 支持 ===\nfcitx5-frontend-gtk4 - GTK4 IM Module for fcitx5\n\n=== 检查 nautilus 可用版本 ===\nnautilus:\n  已安装：1:48.0-1ubuntu1\n  候选： 1:48.0-1ubuntu1\n  版本列表：\n *** 1:48.0-1ubuntu1 500\n        500 http://cn.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu plucky/main amd64 Packages\n        100 /var/lib/dpkg/status","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774579358152}}
{"type":"message","id":"04cdd7c1","parentId":"2a64c1f3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:42:44.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到问题了！nautilus 使用的是 GTK4，而 fcitx 只提供了 GTK2、GTK3、QT5 的 immodule，没有 GTK4 的支持。GTK4 的 immodule 目录只有 ibus。\n\n这是一个兼容性问题。解决方案：\n1. 换用其他文件管理器（如 Thunar、Files (GNOME Files) 的旧版本）\n2. 等搜狗输入法支持 GTK4\n3. 尝试使用 ibus 版本的搜狗\n\n让我检查是否有替代方案，或者看看能否用 GTK3 的方式来解决。\n","thinkingSignature":"0c7fb0a1d2e1eef606a7f7b5609c80fc263777f5e092586db013f3fd5af73d3f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v28f67ido15g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 安装替代文件管理器 ===\" && apt-cache search \"thunar\\|nemo\\|caja\" 2>/dev/null | head -10","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":234,"output":175,"cacheRead":31360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31769,"cost":{"input":0.0000702,"output":0.00020999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0009407999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012209999999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774579358155,"responseId":"0615219e54debcbeb1edee060251e7f4"}}
