{"type":"message","id":"4f4a3986","parentId":"86931c26","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:42:52.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来没有其他文件管理器可用。让我考虑另一个方案：给 nautilus 设置一个环境变量强制使用 GTK3。\n\n或者，我可以尝试在 GTK4 中禁用 IM 模块，让它fallback到 XIM。\n","thinkingSignature":"bbd6ccc2adae9a3b99166a856969c663a9a2d37f9496a2c8687f07a757fa5b7a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_agkedqj7kqf7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 尝试使用 GTK_IM_MODULE=xim 启动 nautilus ===\" && GTK_IM_MODULE=xim QT_IM_MODULE=xim XMODIFIERS=@im=xim nautilus 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\necho \"已用 XIM 模式启动，请在文件管理器中测试重命名是否能输入中文\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":127,"output":143,"cacheRead":31552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31822,"cost":{"input":0.0000381,"output":0.0001716,"cacheRead":0.0009465599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0011562599999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774579365640,"responseId":"061521a5bb4cd955af92765b92f8771f"}}
