{"type":"message","id":"69715772","parentId":"bb6dbc2b","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:20:36.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The chrome is already the latest stable version. Chrome 142 is the latest stable version. Let me explain this to the user and also start the remote debugging.\n","thinkingSignature":"a091147308629e30e916f8be33dc18d1263aad65b78532744300b80812cc59fb"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n小王子，你的 Chrome 已经是最新版本了！🎉\n\n**当前版本**：Google Chrome 142.0.7444.134（最新稳定版）\n\n---\n\n现在帮你打开远程调试功能：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0w01opf4v4e6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pkill -f \"chrome-remote\\|chrome.*remote\" 2>/dev/null; sleep 1; /home/zhangyanbo/bin/chrome-remote-debug.sh 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\necho \"=== 验证 ===\" && curl -s http://127.0.0.1:9222/json/version | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(f'✅ Chrome 已启动，版本: {d[\\\"Browser\\\"]}')\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":107,"output":214,"cacheRead":46784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47105,"cost":{"input":0.0000321,"output":0.0002568,"cacheRead":0.00140352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00169242}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606826224,"responseId":"06158cea3d63fbdcd4f659c8260aa1f8"}}
