{"type":"message","id":"9cf0deea","parentId":"c84f3e67","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:22:34.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！端口监听在 127.0.0.1:9222，但小王子可能是从其他设备访问的（比如他的本地电脑）。从远程访问需要使用 0.0.0.0:9222 或者 Ubuntu 服务器的 IP 地址。\n\n让我检查一下端口绑定情况，并重新启动 Chrome 使用正确的配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"f7a12485a22dfd37925e0c9d21d8b1fbb765a81f49f39cba0dbc6961aba64fe7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bwp68csfq9k4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查端口绑定 ===\" && ss -tlnp | grep 9222 && echo -e \"\\n=== 获取服务器 IP ===\" && hostname -I | awk '{print $1}'","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7900,"output":144,"cacheRead":48128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56172,"cost":{"input":0.0023699999999999997,"output":0.0001728,"cacheRead":0.0014438399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00398664}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606944047,"responseId":"06158d60f49c13f0af9e7295ff7c505f"}}
