{"type":"message","id":"715abf93","parentId":"2c7a059e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:22:46.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！端口绑定的是 127.0.0.1 (本地回环地址)，不是 0.0.0.0。这意味着只能从本机访问，外部无法访问。\n\n虽然启动参数设置了 --remote-debugging-address=0.0.0.0，但似乎 Chrome 忽略了这个设置，仍然只绑定到 127.0.0.1。\n\n让我修改启动脚本，换一种方式来启动 Chrome，确保远程调试地址正确绑定。\n","thinkingSignature":"65bc91fddd006bec5fe52a506018f614ee4bf87545b5be73501dfaa42bfd4ab8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uxnu1dzigchx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 修复：重新启动 Chrome ===\" && pkill -f \"chrome-remote\\|chrome.*remote-debug\" 2>/dev/null; sleep 1\n\n# 使用 --remote-debugging-address=0.0.0.0 重新启动\ngoogle-chrome \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9222 \\\n  --remote-debugging-address=0.0.0.0 \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --user-data-dir=/tmp/chrome-remote-debug-new \\\n  &\n\nsleep 2\necho -e \"\\n=== 验证端口绑定 ===\" && ss -tlnp | grep 9222","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":181,"output":268,"cacheRead":56000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56449,"cost":{"input":0.0000543,"output":0.0003216,"cacheRead":0.0016799999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020559}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606954530,"responseId":"06158d6aa62078e2cb13f87e2c025957"}}
