{"type":"message","id":"c41dd578","parentId":"43270da9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:40:15.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"需要 sudo 密码。让我先告诉用户问题所在，并给他解决方案。\n\n小王子，找到问题了！🎯\n\n**问题原因**：\n你的 Chrome 更新源被禁用了（`Enabled: no`），所以：\n- Chrome 无法通过系统包管理器更新\n- 但 Chrome 内部更新检查仍然工作，会提示有新版本\n\n**当前版本**: 142.0.7444.134（这已经是最新版了）\n\n---\n\n**解决方案**：\n\n**方法 1：手动启用更新源**（需要密码）\n```bash\nsudo sed -i 's/Enabled: no/Enabled: yes/' /etc/apt/sources.list.d/google-chrome.sources\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install google-chrome-stable\n```\n\n**方法 2：在 Chrome 中禁用更新提示**\n1. 打开 Chrome\n2. 地址栏输入：`chrome://settings/help`\n3. 如果显示\"Chrome 已是最新版本\"，更新提示会消失\n\n---\n\n**Chrome 已经打开了**，你可以在浏览器中访问 `chrome://settings/help` 检查更新状态。\n\n需要我帮你启用更新源吗？需要你的 sudo 密码 🔐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":263,"cacheRead":84046,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":84487,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007364,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000743}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774608010311,"responseId":"msg_b21e3e30-e7da-42b7-b7a6-163ea2cd161d"}}
