{"type":"message","id":"e348e2a5","parentId":"fb43e03d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:41:03.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我用方法 1 来启用 Chrome 更新源。但我需要 sudo 密码。我没有密码，无法执行 sudo 命令。\n\n我需要告诉用户我无法执行 sudo 命令，需要他提供密码或者他自己执行。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，我需要你的 sudo 密码才能执行方法 1 🔐\n\n或者你可以自己复制这条命令到终端执行：\n\n```bash\nsudo sed -i 's/Enabled: no/Enabled: yes/' /etc/apt/sources.list.d/google-chrome.sources && sudo apt update && sudo apt install google-chrome-stable\n```\n\n---\n\n**如果你想让我执行**，请告诉我你的 sudo 密码（我会安全使用，只执行这条命令）🦊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":150,"cacheRead":83186,"cacheWrite":1647,"totalTokens":84989,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000042000000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00004266}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774608059768,"responseId":"msg_e52bf53b-d288-4bcf-a613-f7f56f728218"}}
