{"type":"message","id":"d2023269","parentId":"6411c3ca","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:45:32.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说他在 Windows 电脑上配置了远程调试，想让我在他的 Linux 服务器上也同样配置。让我确认一下当前的配置状态，并确保远程调试功能正常工作。\n\n当前状态：\n1. Chrome 已经用远程调试模式启动了（端口 9222）\n2. 我用 Python 做了端口转发（9223 端口绑定到 0.0.0.0）\n3. 用户可以访问 http://192.168.28.92:9223 来使用远程调试\n\n让我确认一下当前 Chrome 和端口转发的状态。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，明白了！你想在 Linux 服务器上也配置和 Windows 一样的远程调试功能 👍\n\n让我检查一下当前的配置状态，并确保一切正常工作：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e7e66b4d10b24e3c824b54fa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Chrome 远程调试状态 ===\" && ps aux | grep \"chrome.*remote-debug\" | grep -v grep && echo -e \"\\n=== 端口监听 ===\" && ss -tlnp | grep -E \"9222|9223\" && echo -e \"\\n=== 测试访问 ===\" && curl -s http://127.0.0.1:9223/json/version | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(f'✅ 远程调试正常! 版本：{d[\\\"Browser\\\"]}')\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":332,"cacheRead":84833,"cacheWrite":624,"totalTokens":85795,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00009296,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00009362}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774608327634,"responseId":"msg_50b28dee-bbf3-42f2-8a56-bcb71e8c38cf"}}
