{"type":"message","id":"3390ae1c","parentId":"363651e8","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:46:26.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"小王子，配置好了！🎉\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 已完成的配置\n\n**1. Chrome 远程调试已启动**\n- 端口：9222（本地）\n- 转发端口：9223（外部访问）\n\n**2. 访问地址**\n```\nhttp://192.168.28.92:9223\n```\n\n**3. 启动脚本**\n创建了快捷脚本 `/home/zhangyanbo/bin/chrome-remote-debug.sh`\n- 以后需要重启时，运行这个脚本即可\n- 会自动启动 Chrome 和端口转发\n\n---\n\n## 📋 和 Windows 配置对比\n\n| 功能 | Windows | Linux（你的服务器） |\n|------|---------|-------------------|\n| Chrome 远程调试 | ✅ | ✅ |\n| 端口转发 | ✅ | ✅ |\n| 外部访问 | `IP:9222` | `IP:9223` |\n\n---\n\n现在你可以在其他设备的浏览器访问 `http://192.168.28.92:9223`，就能看到所有可调试的标签页了！🦊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":263,"cacheRead":86644,"cacheWrite":574,"totalTokens":87487,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007364,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000743}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774608382067,"responseId":"msg_ec84cc35-182f-4867-9b1f-2d579131265c"}}
