{"type":"message","id":"e538bd8a","parentId":"3a280560","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:47:10.757Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要把端口也改成 9222，和 Windows 一样。我需要：\n1. 杀掉当前的 Chrome 和端口转发进程\n2. 重新启动 Chrome，让它直接绑定到 0.0.0.0:9222\n\n但是之前我尝试过，Chrome 的 --remote-debugging-address=0.0.0.0 参数在某些 Linux 环境中不生效，它仍然会绑定到 127.0.0.1。\n\n不过让我再试一次，或者用 iptables 来做端口映射，把外部访问的 9222 映射到 127.0.0.1:9222。\n\n或者用 socat/iptables 来做 DNAT。\n\n让我尝试用 iptables 来做端口映射。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，明白了！你想用 9222 端口，和 Windows 一样 👍\n\n但是 Chrome 在 Linux 上有个限制：即使设置了 `--remote-debugging-address=0.0.0.0`，它仍然只绑定到 127.0.0.1。\n\n让我用 iptables 来做端口映射，把外部的 9222 映射到内部的 9222：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4c4c6e5515354d0c9d47497a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 停止当前服务 ===\" && pkill -f \"chrome.*remote\" 2>/dev/null; pkill -f \"python3.*9223\" 2>/dev/null; sleep 1\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 启动 Chrome ===\" && google-chrome \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9222 \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --user-data-dir=/tmp/chrome-remote-debug \\\n  &\n\nsleep 3\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 用 iptables 做端口映射（外部 9222 -> 内部 9222）===\" && sudo iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -p tcp --dport 9222 -j DNAT --to-destination 127.0.0.1:9222 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":502,"cacheRead":85457,"cacheWrite":2378,"totalTokens":88343,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00014056000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00014122000000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774608417794,"responseId":"msg_36293cf2-a648-430b-8166-fe39c248cf0a"}}
