{"type":"message","id":"f6a2aa36","parentId":"e8d280e8","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:47:51.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Chrome 启动了，但是仍然绑定到 127.0.0.1:9222。我需要用 iptables 或者其他方法把外部访问的 9222 端口映射到 127.0.0.1:9222。\n\niptables 需要 sudo 权限，让我试试看能不能执行。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Chrome 启动了，但还是绑定在 127.0.0.1:9222。让我尝试用 iptables 做端口映射：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b6a7f0beb31e4bf4bde59a02","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 尝试用 iptables 做端口映射 ===\" && sudo iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -p tcp --dport 9222 -j DNAT --to-destination 127.0.0.1:9222 && echo \"✅ iptables 规则已添加\" && sudo iptables -t nat -L PREROUTING -n -v | grep 9222","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":245,"cacheRead":88750,"cacheWrite":274,"totalTokens":89275,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0000686,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006926}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774608467461,"responseId":"msg_ed9924c3-c6dd-4c6c-8f3c-9666a889fd54"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9e78589","parentId":"f6a2aa36","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:47:51.342Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_b6a7f0beb31e4bf4bde59a02","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 尝试用 iptables 做端口映射 ===\nsudo: a terminal is required to read the password; either use the -S option to read from standard input or configure an askpass helper\nsudo: 需要密码\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"=== 尝试用 iptables 做端口映射 ===\nsudo: a terminal is required to read the password; either use the -S option to read from standard input or configure an askpass helper\nsudo: 需要密码\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774608471338}}
{"type":"message","id":"67cf65bb","parentId":"e9e78589","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:47:58.590Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"iptables 需要 sudo 密码。让我尝试另一种方法 - 用 socat 来做端口转发，把 0.0.0.0:9222 转发到 127.0.0.1:9222。\n\n但是 9222 已经被 Chrome 占用了，我需要用另一个端口，或者先让 Chrome 用其他端口。\n\n让我换个思路：\n1. 让 Chrome 绑定到 127.0.0.1:9221\n2. 用 socat/python 把 0.0.0.0:9222 转发到 127.0.0.1:9221\n\n这样外部访问 9222 端口就能访问到 Chrome 了。\niptables 需要密码。让我换个方法 - 让 Chrome 用其他端口，然后用端口转发把 9222 映射过去：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9e84bf53b80b4818ad76978d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pkill -9 chrome 2>/dev/null; sleep 1\n\necho \"=== 启动 Chrome 到 9221 端口 ===\" && google-chrome \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9221 \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --user-data-dir=/tmp/chrome-remote-debug \\\n  &\n\nsleep 3\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 启动端口转发 (0.0.0.0:9222 -> 127.0.0.1:9221) ===\" && nohup python3 -c \"\nimport socket\nimport threading\ns = socket.socket(socket.AF_INET, socket.SOCK_STREAM)\ns.setsockopt(socket.SOL_SOCKET, socket.SO_REUSEADDR, 1)\ns.bind(('0.0.0.0', 9222))\ns.listen(5)\nprint('Port forward: 0.0.0.0:9222 -> 127.0.0.1:9221', flush=True)\nwhile True:\n    c, a = s.accept()\n    t = socket.socket(socket.AF_INET, socket.SOCK_STREAM)\n    t.connect(('127.0.0.1', 9221))\n    def go(src, dst):\n        while 1:\n            try: dst.send(src.recv(4096))\n            except: break\n        src.close()\n        dst.close()\n    threading.Thread(target=go, args=(c, t), daemon=True).start()\n    threading.Thread(target=go, args=(t, c), daemon=True).start()\n\" > /tmp/pf9222.log 2>&1 &\n\nsleep 2\necho -e \"\\n=== 验证 ===\" && ss -tlnp | grep -E \"9221|9222\"","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":662,"cacheRead":89024,"cacheWrite":313,"totalTokens":90005,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00018536,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00018602}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774608471343,"responseId":"msg_0a23c994-8faf-491a-a31d-e8a6dcce2acc"}}
