{"type":"message","id":"3e2e9b19","parentId":"f18be89f","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:48:20.198Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_8692957e90d94ab2bbaf0c0c","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 启动 Chrome 到 9221 端口 ===\n\n=== 启动端口转发 (0.0.0.0:9222 -> 127.0.0.1:9221) ===\n\n=== 验证 ===\nLISTEN 0      5                 0.0.0.0:9222       0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"python3\",pid=1606972,fd=3))         \nLISTEN 0      10              127.0.0.1:9221       0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"chrome\",pid=1606845,fd=93))\n\nDevTools listening on ws://127.0.0.1:9221/devtools/browser/15480195-dd59-474f-90e9-9de65e4ec96b\nCreated TensorFlow Lite XNNPACK delegate for CPU.\n[1606845:1606873:0327/184802.406653:ERROR:google_apis/gcm/engine/registration_request.cc:292] Registration response error message: DEPRECATED_ENDPOINT\n\nProcess still running."}],"details":{"status":"running","sessionId":"amber-willow","aggregated":"=== 启动 Chrome 到 9221 端口 ===\n\nDevTools listening on ws://127.0.0.1:9221/devtools/browser/15480195-dd59-474f-90e9-9de65e4ec96b\nCreated TensorFlow Lite XNNPACK delegate for CPU.\n[1606845:1606873:0327/184802.406653:ERROR:google_apis/gcm/engine/registration_request.cc:292] Registration response error message: DEPRECATED_ENDPOINT\n\n=== 启动端口转发 (0.0.0.0:9222 -> 127.0.0.1:9221) ===\n\n=== 验证 ===\nLISTEN 0      5                 0.0.0.0:9222       0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"python3\",pid=1606972,fd=3))         \nLISTEN 0      10              127.0.0.1:9221       0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"chrome\",pid=1606845,fd=93))         \n","name":"pkill chrome","retryInMs":5000},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774608500192}}
{"type":"message","id":"de5665c9","parentId":"3e2e9b19","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:48:28.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功了！现在：\n- Chrome 绑定到 127.0.0.1:9221\n- Python 端口转发把 0.0.0.0:9222 转发到 127.0.0.1:9221\n\n外部访问 192.168.28.92:9222 就能访问到 Chrome 远程调试了！\n\n现在让我更新启动脚本。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"成功了！🎉\n\n现在配置好了：\n- **Chrome** 运行在 127.0.0.1:9221\n- **端口转发** 把 0.0.0.0:9222 → 127.0.0.1:9221\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 访问地址\n\n**http://192.168.28.92:9222**\n\n和 Windows 一样的端口了！👍\n\n---\n\n让我更新启动脚本：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_005c583ae7064ba9bf8a415f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Chrome 远程调试启动脚本（端口 9222）\n\n# 杀掉旧进程\npkill -f \"chrome.*remote-debug\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -f \"python3.*922\" 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\n\n# 启动 Chrome（使用 9221 端口）\ngoogle-chrome \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9221 \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --user-data-dir=/tmp/chrome-remote-debug \\\n  &\n\n# 等待 Chrome 启动\nsleep 3\n\n# 启动端口转发（外部 9222 -> 内部 9221）\nnohup python3 -c \"\nimport socket\nimport threading\ns = socket.socket(socket.AF_INET, socket.SOCK_STREAM)\ns.setsockopt(socket.SOL_SOCKET, socket.SO_REUSEADDR, 1)\ns.bind(('0.0.0.0', 9222))\ns.listen(5)\nwhile True:\n    c, a = s.accept()\n    t = socket.socket(socket.AF_INET, socket.SOCK_STREAM)\n    t.connect(('127.0.0.1', 9221))\n    def go(src, dst):\n        while 1:\n            try: dst.send(src.recv(4096))\n            except: break\n        src.close()\n        dst.close()\n    threading.Thread(target=go, args=(c, t), daemon=True).start()\n    threading.Thread(target=go, args=(t, c), daemon=True).start()\n\" > /tmp/chrome-portforward.log 2>&1 &\n\necho \"✅ Chrome 远程调试已启动！\"\necho \"访问地址：http://$(hostname -I | awk '{print $1}'):9222\"\n","path":"/home/zhangyanbo/bin/chrome-remote-debug.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":685,"cacheRead":90050,"cacheWrite":378,"totalTokens":91119,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0001918,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00019246}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774608500201,"responseId":"msg_aa0ef41c-2773-457b-bc22-852c07439399"}}
