{"type":"message","id":"71ca0ca6","parentId":"d2ab0cd0","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:56:42.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户选择了方案 1，使用他已有的 Chrome 配置文件。我需要：\n\n1. 先找到用户默认的 Chrome 用户数据目录\n2. 关闭当前的远程调试 Chrome\n3. 用用户的默认配置文件重新启动 Chrome 远程调试\n\nChrome 的默认用户数据目录通常在 ~/.config/google-chrome/Default\n\n让我先检查当前的 Chrome 用户数据目录，然后关闭现有的 Chrome，用默认配置文件重新启动。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，好的！让我用你已有的 Chrome 配置文件来启动远程调试：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_47d38373a5f747e6bf3bcaf7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 关闭当前 Chrome ===\" && pkill -9 chrome 2>/dev/null && sleep 2\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 检查你的 Chrome 用户数据目录 ===\" && ls -la ~/.config/google-chrome/ | head -10\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 使用默认配置文件启动 Chrome 远程调试 ===\" && google-chrome \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9221 \\\n  --user-data-dir=/home/zhangyanbo/.config/google-chrome \\\n  &\n\nsleep 5\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 验证 Chrome 已启动 ===\" && ss -tlnp | grep 9221","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":291,"cacheRead":108484,"cacheWrite":750,"totalTokens":109531,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008214}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774608997826,"responseId":"msg_eb51c1ed-7b8f-4498-80c1-575edf608725"}}
