{"type":"message","id":"ab98cf2d","parentId":"d8ce8376","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:57:24.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"远程调试端口 9221 似乎没有正常工作。这可能是因为 Chrome 不允许在默认配置文件上启用远程调试。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：复制你的默认配置文件到一个新目录，然后用这个新目录启动远程调试。这样既能保留你的登录状态和扩展，又能启用远程调试。\n\n让我操作一下：小王子，远程调试端口 9221 没有正常工作，因为 Chrome 不允许直接在默认配置文件上启用远程调试。\n\n让我用另一种方法：**复制你的默认配置文件到新目录**，这样既能保留你的登录状态，又能启用远程调试：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d28d5703da1b4e68a4b1a6d6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 关闭 Chrome ===\" && pkill -9 chrome && sleep 2\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 复制默认配置文件到新目录 ===\" && rm -rf /tmp/chrome-user-data && cp -r ~/.config/google-chrome/Default /tmp/chrome-user-data/Default && echo \"✅ 配置文件已复制\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 用复制的配置文件启动 Chrome 远程调试 ===\" && google-chrome \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9221 \\\n  --user-data-dir=/tmp/chrome-user-data \\\n  &\n\nsleep 5\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 验证 ===\" && curl -s http://127.0.0.1:9221/json/version | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(f'✅ 成功！Browser: {d[\\\"Browser\\\"]}')\"","timeout":25}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":355,"cacheRead":113486,"cacheWrite":154,"totalTokens":114001,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0000994,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010006}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774609040065,"responseId":"msg_1115144a-033c-46f2-954d-a2cd87ef6f25"}}
